summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Water Department and granting King County Water District No. 108 permission to install sanitary sewers across the Lake Youngs Bypass Line 4 in the vicinity of its intersections with 140th Avenue S.E. and 151st Avenue S.E., and across the Lake Youngs Tunnel right of way in the vicinity of 140th Avenue S.E., King County, Washington and specifying the terms.
